Scientists figure out how to do teleportation, instantaneously swapping two equal volumes, but the limitation is that they don&rsquo;t have any control over where one of the samples is from. Because most volumes in the universe are total vacuum, this is essentially an incredible kinetic weapon. It becomes more and more common, replacing TNT, since (by lowering the volume) you can finely tune the amount of force. However, one day, an implosion goes wrong during a controlled demolition and it&rsquo;s discovered that we have accidentally teleported half of a large living alien being. This is our first contact.
